  <title>SENIOR LABORATORY TECHNICIAN</title>
  <link>https://www.ub.bw/connect/job-opportunities/senior-laboratory-technician</link>
  <description>&lt;span class="field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden"&gt;SENIOR LABORATORY TECHNICIAN&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="field field--name-uid field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden"&gt;&lt;a title="View user profile." href="https://www.ub.bw/user/2371" lang="" about="https://www.ub.bw/user/2371" typeof="schema:Person" property="schema:name" datatype="" class="username" xml:lang=""&gt;mfetane&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="field field--name-created field--type-created field--label-hidden"&gt;Mon, 11/03/2024 - 08:45&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;div class="field field--name-field-department field--type-entity-reference field--label-inline clearfix"&gt;
    &lt;div class="field__label"&gt;Department/Faculty&lt;/div&gt;
              &lt;div class="field__item"&gt;Chemistry&lt;/div&gt;
          &lt;/div&gt;

  &lt;div class="field field--name-field-tender-closing-date field--type-datetime field--label-inline clearfix"&gt;
    &lt;div class="field__label"&gt;Closing Date&lt;/div&gt;
              &lt;div class="field__item"&gt;Wed, 27 Mar. 2024&lt;/div&gt;
          &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field__item"&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;FACULTY OF SCIENCE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;DEPARTMENT OF &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;CHEMISTRY&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;VACANCY NO: IRC 1237&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Duties&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The successful candidate will be expected to &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;(i) &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;deputize for Chief Technician when required; (ii) manage laboratories daily e.g. do preparations for laboratory practicals, delegation of duties, supervision and training of subordinate staff, the senior technician will  oversee the smooth running of laboratories; (iii) act as  a Safety Officer for the Department and report to the Chief Technician; (iv) maintain high productivity in the laboratories; (v) demonstrate, where appropriately competent, the use of laboratory equipment and experiment techniques to students; (vi) do stocktaking of laboratory supplies and advises in the purchase of the same.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Requirements: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;A minimum of a Higher Diploma or Degree in Chemistry or related field, PLUS at least two (2) years post qualification relevant experience.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;OR &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;at least three (3) years of service at the level of Technician, excluding the period of full-time study and a record of outstanding service.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Knowledge and experience in the operation of scientific laboratory equipment will be an added advantage.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Remuneration:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;  The University offers a competitive salary and benefits commensurate with qualifications and experience.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Applicants are to address the stated qualification in their application letters and provide other information to assist the University determine their suitability for the position. They should also quote the vacancy number of the post applied for, provide current CVs (including telephone, telefax and e-mail), certified copies of educational certificates and transcripts, names and addresses of three referees. Complete documentation should be sent to: The Human Resources Manager, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Faculty of Science, University of Botswana Private Bag UB 00704, Gaborone, Botswana; Telephone: (267) 355 4937/2969; Fax (267) 318 5097; E-mail: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;a href="mailto:fosvacancies@ub.ac.bw."&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;fosvacancies@ub.ac.bw.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Applicants should inform their referees to (i) &lt;strong&gt;quote the vacancy number and position applied for&lt;/strong&gt; and (ii) &lt;strong&gt;submit their references directly to the above address before the stipulated date&lt;/strong&gt;. Please note that applications with incomplete information shall not be acknowledged.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Hand delivered applications should be submitted to Block &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt;233, Office 135 (233/135).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;NB:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; Only shortlisted applicants will be contacted.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Closing date:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;  27 March 2024&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

